msgstr "Esitamise ajal näita meediavoo teavet"

msgid ""
"Something went wrong loading radio stations data from station provider. "
"Please try again later."
msgstr ""
"Raadiojaamade teabe laadimisel teenusepakkujalt läks midagi valesti. Palun "
"proovi hiljem uuesti."

